<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Libreria No tan cercana</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/uikit@3.5.4/dist/css/uikit.min.css" />
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/uikit@3.5.4/dist/js/uikit.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/uikit@3.5.4/dist/js/uikit-icons.min.js"></script>
  </head>
  <div class="containerDelBody" >
  <body>
    <h2 class ="uk-text-lead">Recomendados</h2>
   
    <div class="uk-position-relative uk-visible-toggle uk-light" tabindex="-1" uk-slider>
     
      <ul class="uk-slider-items uk-child-width-1-2 uk-child-width-1-3@m uk-grid">
        <% books.forEach(book => { %>
           
          <div class="uk-width-1-4">
        <li>
              <div class="uk-panel">
                <a href="/books/<%= book.id %>">
                  
              
                  <img src="<%= book.image %>" alt="book photo">
                  <div class="uk-position-bottom uk-panel"></div>
                  
                </a>
                <p class="clase-subtitulo"><%= book.title %></p>
              </div>
          </li>
          </div>
          <% }) %>
          
      </ul>
      <ul class="uk-slider-nav uk-dotnav uk-flex-center uk-margin"></ul>
      <a class="uk-position-center-left uk-position-small uk-hidden-hover" href="#" uk-slidenav-previous uk-slider-item="previous"></a>
      <a class="uk-position-center-right uk-position-small uk-hidden-hover" href="#" uk-slidenav-next uk-slider-item="next"></a>
  
  </div>

  <hr class="uk-divider-icon">
  <h2 class ="uk-text-lead">Novedades</h2>
  <div class="uk-position-relative uk-visible-toggle uk-light" tabindex="-1" uk-slider>
     
    <ul class="uk-slider-items uk-child-width-1-2 uk-child-width-1-3@m uk-grid">
      <% books.forEach(book => { %>
         
        <div class="uk-width-1-6">
      <li>
            <div class="uk-panel">
              <a href="/books/<%= book.id %>">
                
            
                <img src="<%= book.image %>" alt="book photo">
                
              </a>
              <p class="clase-subtitulo"><%= book.title %></p>
            </div>
        </li>
        </div>
        <% }) %>
        
    </ul>
    <ul class="uk-slider-nav uk-dotnav uk-flex-center uk-margin"></ul>
    <a class="uk-position-center-left uk-position-small uk-hidden-hover" href="#" uk-slidenav-previous uk-slider-item="previous"></a>
    <a class="uk-position-center-right uk-position-small uk-hidden-hover" href="#" uk-slidenav-next uk-slider-item="next"></a>

</div>

  <hr class="uk-divider-icon">
  
  <div class="uk-card uk-card-default uk-grid-collapse uk-child-width-1-2@s uk-margin" uk-grid>
    <div class="uk-card-media-left uk-cover-container">
        <img src="images/murakami.jpg" alt="murakami" uk-cover>
        <canvas width="400" height="400"></canvas>
    </div>
    <div>
        <div class="uk-card-body">
            <h3 class="uk-card-title">Autor del mes de junio: Haruki Murakami</h3>
            <p>Lo elegimos autor del mes por su basta trayectoria en Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dolorum, voluptatibus cum odio aut molestiae et! Expedita ipsa perspiciatis, dolor culpa numquam minus placeat architecto natus odit nesciunt fugiat. Voluptas, corporis?.</p>
      
          
        <div class="uk-position-relative  uk-visible-toggle uk-light" tabindex="-1" uk-slider>
     
          <ul class="uk-slider-items uk-child-width-1-2 uk-child-width-1-3@m uk-grid">
            <% books.forEach(book => { %>
               
              <div class="uk-width-1-4">
            <li>
                  <div class="uk-panel">
                    <a href="/books/<%= book.id %>">
                      
                  
                      <img src="<%= book.image %>" alt="book photo">
                    
                    </a>
                    <p class="clase-subtitulo"><%= book.title %></p>
                  </div>
              </li>
              </div>
              <% }) %>
              
          </ul>
          <ul class="uk-slider-nav uk-dotnav uk-flex-center uk-margin"></ul>
          <a class="uk-position-top-left uk-position-small uk-hidden-hover" href="#" uk-slidenav-previous uk-slider-item="previous"></a>
          <a class="uk-position-center-right uk-position-small uk-hidden-hover" href="#" uk-slidenav-next uk-slider-item="next"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

<hr class="uk-divider-icon">
<h2 class ="uk-text-lead uk-text-center">Categorías Recomendadas para vos</h2>

<div class="uk-child-width-1-3@m uk-grid-small uk-grid-match" uk-grid>
  <div>
    <a href="/books/arte">
      <div class="uk-card uk-card-default uk-card-body">
          <h3 class="uk-card-title">Arte</h3>
          <p>Tremenda Categoría 1</p>
       </a>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <a href="/books/narrativa">
      <div class="uk-card uk-card-primary uk-card-body">
          <h3 class="uk-card-title">Narrativa</h3>
          <p>Tremenda Categoría 2</p>
        </a>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <a href="/books/ensayo">
      <div class="uk-card uk-card-secondary uk-card-body">
          <h3 class="uk-card-title">Ensayos</h3>
          <p>Tremenda Categoría 3</p>
         </a>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>
  </body>
</div>
</html>

